00:39.545 --> 00:48.013
I'm a respectable citizen, you know, so I'll kind of take their part in complaining about it.

00:48.113 --> 00:52.076
And that's kind of when I saw the attitude.

00:53.117 --> 00:57.241
Yes, at that point, yes.

